text: "They set you up real nice eh. Not so sure about the color scheme though. Could use a little more...red. At least in my opinion."
"I don't think it needs any more red."
"Did you forget? You have a doctor's appointment. I'm here to pick you up."
"Go fuck yourself that's not why you're here."
"Haha. That's rich. You come into MY home and tell ME to leave? That's not how this works fucko."
"Hey, you really need to take a chill pill." (maybe even 2 pills of chill)
"I'm thinking that's exactly how this works."
"Nothing to say? Haha. Wow you really are pathetic. Guess I can't compete with you on that front. Whatever, do me a favor and close your eyes yeah? It's time to end this."
"Can you? I don't know if we can trust you to handle this on your own. Why don't we have have a little race hm? Let's see who can get you to the doctor first."
"It'll be a quick trip. Let me just make sure you're up to date on your shots first..."
"Not really. I do have a particular shade in mind though."
"I'm not talking about recoloring the whole apartment. I think 5 liters will be enough."
"Oh you like doing pills too? Come here I got some pills for you."
"Let's put your little theory to the test them hm?"
